## Legal Reporting Notes

All findings were documented in a forensically sound report prepared for civil litigation and potential criminal referral under the **Information Technology Act, 2000 (Section 43 & 66)** and **Indian Penal Code Section 378 (theft of data)**.

- Chain of custody documentation completed for all 3 exhibits
- Hashes verified at acquisition, during analysis, and at report completion
- Expert witness statement prepared for civil court proceedings
- Google Drive preservation request submitted to Google India legal team

