## Recommendations

| Finding | Recommendation |
|---------|---------------|
| DLP bypassed via hidden folder | Extend MDM DLP scanning to all directories including hidden paths |
| No alert on 4+ GB upload | Implement cloud upload size alerts (threshold: >500 MB in single session) |
| USB OTG unrestricted | Enforce MDM policy: disable USB OTG on all company devices |
| After-hours exfiltration undetected | Enable off-hours data access alerting via CASB |
| No pre-departure access review | Implement automatic access reduction 30 days before known departure |
